hink about REST without hypermedia, it will not be problem. But it
seems li=
ke REST depends on using hypermedia, right?



If you believe so and want =
your consumers to use hypermedia, using a
Java framework, you have to rely =
on Restfulie, Jersey and Restlet, who
are trying to do so.



As Paul ment=
ioned, its a matter of time for it to enter the JAX-RS
